Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:03.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started with the Sacred Tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:05.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting and searching\nforourdreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a strong bond\nis formed between us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:08.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new hope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bright future begins now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:13.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango is unaware that\NKohaku has regained his memory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:16.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Kirara knows just what both\nof them are feeling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:18.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the village of the Demon Slayers\nwhich holds so many memories,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:19.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a miracle occurs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:21.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final shard guides us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:22.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other side of the well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:24.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a new day awaits in\nthe age of warring states!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:25.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:26.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:06.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango's younger brother, Kohaku,\nis caught in Naraku's contemptible trap{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:08.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and must beara heavy burden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And even now, Kohaku continues\nto be manipulated by him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:19.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango feels an enormous guilt\nthat she is responsible,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:22.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and we want to do something\nforher...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:24.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it doesn't seem to be\nthat simple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonderwhat Kirara\nis thinking about Kohaku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup, it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder where Kirara has gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:03:00.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara can manage alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:03.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But lately, Kirara goes off\non her own quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:06.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is close to Sango's\nbirthplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so she probably feels\nvery nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:47.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't find Kikyo\naround here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Try somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just make sure you don't\nget killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:05.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Same goes forme.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:35.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:37.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's going towards you, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boy, it's begun to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here, you'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:46.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay back, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Try to bearit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:23.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:37.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:54.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0} Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:55.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forme?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:04.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:07.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:56.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Kagome, it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:58.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kirara....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:00.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:03.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, come have tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:08.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Sango!\NIt's no use getting all fidgety!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:12.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Kirara is the most\nreliable one among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But she's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:17.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya you {\i1}know....{\i0}\NThe demon slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All alone today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:15.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:22.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here, Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, huh, Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Sisterwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:49.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:01.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But right now, I can't go back\nto Sisteryet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Demon Slayer, do you\nknow where {\i1}Kikyo....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Kohaku with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He is, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:14.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}wonder....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're that worried,\nwhy don't you search for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:21.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you intend to do\nwhen you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you find him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he's bound to Naraku until\nhe dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said it has nothing to do\nwith you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:45.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Many people have {\i1}died....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why the least I can do\nis avenge {\i1}theirdeaths....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and kill Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I {\i1}will....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'll succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I don't know if I deserve\nto live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:31.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:38.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We fought so hard\nand now, we're exhausted!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demon Slayers\nare so strong...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:46.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too bad forthe demons!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:11.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay {\i1}still....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:47.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey {\i1}Kirara....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:49.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll show you my secret place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:02.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not much time has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:04.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He must be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:09.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you intend to do\nwhen you see him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:27.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku is still my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This spot hasn't changed\na bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:53.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish I could have shown it\nto Sister, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:05.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku... Kohaku... Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:07.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:10.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say hello to Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:35.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:47.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:26.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:44.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:55.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara?\NYou want me to follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:03.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kirara....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just {\i1}what....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Agarden of {\i1}lilies....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:33.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}injury....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:36.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have medicine on {\i1}it....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:34.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.83,0:23:48.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo falls underthe spell\nof a parasite chrysalis!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:51.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's become a violent prankster\nand that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.17,0:23:53.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:55.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The villagers are seething mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:57.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to find him\nbefore he gets exterminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.78,0:24:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid! Your Fox-fire isn't hot at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.95,0:24:04.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I still have othertricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.39,0:24:09.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Possessed by a Parasite:\NShippo, Our Worst Enemy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.72,0:24:12.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you keep pulling\nyourfox pranks on me?!
